 Nigerian rapper, Olanrewaju Fasasi fondly called Sound Sultan has shared a stunning photo of his family as they mark the Eid-el-fitr celebration. Sound Sultan also refuted claims that was speculating social media about he being ill with throat cancer. He described the news as fake. In a fresh Instagram post, the 44 year old Nigerian songwriter sent wished to Muslims who were celebrating their feast. He also extended love to his fans while debunking the news of his ailment, he wrote;
EID MUBARAK TO MY LOVELY Muslim brothers and sisters . .MAY ALMIGHTY ALLAH ACCEPT OUR FAST As an act of Ibadah. INSTAGRAM !!! THIS IS NOT THE ONE WITH RAM .. I must not ignore the massive show of love .THANK YOU ALL. I will tell you my story myself it will be true THEN not false